Program: Discovery
Title: The direction of the Universe
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwwh
Last Broadcast Date: 21 April 1997
New theories on the direction of the Universe. Using radio waves astronomers were able to calculate the distance and the direction of distance galaxies. Also, the gene test that can detect cancer and the development of high yielding wheat. Presenter: Martin Redfern